title: State-Sponsored Terrorism, Crimes, Lies-Collection 30 (Russia 6)
description:
State-Sponsored Terrorism, Crimes, and Lies - Collection 30 (Russia 6):

We have 28 titles here.  One title that deserves a special mention is: "Winter Is Coming; Why Vladimir Putin and the Enemies of the Free World Must Be Stopped (2015)", written by Gary Kasparov, the previous chess world champion. It is a must-read.
Included also is the WADA report that exposed the wide-use of performance enhancing drugs among Russian athletes.

-  Applebaum - Iron Curtain; the Crushing of Eastern Europe, 1945-1956 (2012)

-  Balmaceda (Ed.) - On the Edge; Ukrainian-Central European-Russian Security Triangle (2000)
